INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("56", "1", "2015-01-20 17:19:20", "2015-01-20 17:19:20", "<div class=\"super-hero benefits\">\r\n 	\r\n	<div class=\"super-hero-inner\">\r\n			<div class=\"super-hero-callout\">\r\n				<h2>CaregiverHQ Is Here For You,<br>So You Can Be There For Them.</h2>\r\n                                <p>Caring for a loved one means facing many difficult, stressful decisions that can weigh on your mind. Sometimes it may feel like a caregiver’s duties are never done. Each day brings about a new task list, and sometimes it can be overwhelming trying to balance everything you need to do. We know how selfless being a caregiver is, and that taking time for yourself may feel selfish to you. Let our experts lend you a helping hand to lift some of the burden off your shoulders and provide the caregiver support you deserve every step of the way.</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n	<div class=\"left-half benefits-one\"></div>\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"right-half\">\r\n             <div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"title\"><h2>Personal Care Coach</h2></div>\r\n		<div class=\"block\"><p>You’ll be paired with a Personal Care Coach, a licensed social worker who meets your specific needs. Together, you’ll set achievable goals that your coach will proactively help you meet. When you’re not feeling wholly yourself, you’re not giving your whole self to any aspect of your life. With a Personal Care Coach available to counsel you, you can get back on track to a healthier, happier you.</p></div>\r\n             </div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"left-half\">\r\n             <div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"title\"><h2>Personal Caregiving Roadmap</h2></div>\r\n		<div class=\"block\"><p>Options for your loved one can seem endless. Our experts have answers to your questions – both logistical and emotional – so you can rest assured that you’r