INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("110", "1", "2015-01-25 14:38:53", "2015-01-25 14:38:53", "<div id=\"container\" class=\"hfeed\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"super-hero home\">\r\n 	\r\n	<div class=\"super-hero-inner\">\r\n			<div class=\"super-hero-callout\">\r\n				<h5>Your parents didn\'t raise a caregiver.</h5>\r\n				<h1>They raised a person who cares.</h1>\r\n			</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"provides-frame\">\r\n 	\r\n	<div class=\"provides-frame-inner\">\r\n			<div class=\"super-hero-callout\">\r\n				<p><span class=\"custom\">At</span> <span class=\"branded\">CaregiverHQ</span> <span class=\"custom\">, we provide our caregivers with high-quality support, guidance, resources, and a variety of personal solutions &mdash; because everyone matters. Let CaregiverHQ care for you. </span></p>\r\n				\r\n			</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n	<div id=\"one\" class=\"left-half benefits-one\"></div>\r\n\r\n	<div id=\"two\" class=\"right-half\">\r\n             <div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"title\"><h2>Personal Care Coach</h2></div>\r\n		<div class=\"block\"><p>You&#39;ll be paired with a Personal Care Coach, a licensed social worker who meets your specific needs. Together, you&#39;ll set achievable goals that your coach will proactively help you meet. When you&#39;re not feeling wholly yourself, you&#39;re not giving your whole self to any aspect of your life. With a Personal Care Coach available to counsel you, you can get back on track to a healthier, happier you.</p></div>\r\n             </div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n        <div id=\"three\" class=\"left-half\">\r\n             <div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"title\"><h2>Personal Caregiving Roadmap</h2></div>\r\n		<div class=\"block\"><p>Options for your loved one can seem endless. Our experts have answers to your questions &mdash; both logistical and emotional &mdash; so you can rest assured that you&#39;re doing the right thing. Your care coach will create a &#34;personal caregiving roadmap&#34; to help you navigate through these options and plan to meet specific goals. We want to make sure your work as a caregiver is manageable and that you&#39;re providing the best possible care you can give.</p></div>	\r\n             </div>						\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div id=\"four\" class=\"right-half benefits-two\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n	<div id=\"five\" class=\"left-half benefits-three\"></div>\r\n\r\n	<div id=\"six\" class=\"right-half\">\r\n             <div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"title\"><h2>Premium Service Network</h2></div>\r\n		<div class=\"block\"><p>You may need a variety of services for your loved one &mdash; from in-home help to legal guidance. We know you may not have the time to research all of the services available in your area, so your Personal Care Coach will connect you to our network of service providers who have been evaluated by CaregiverHQ to guarantee the highest level of care.  </p></div>	\r\n             </div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"hear-what\">\r\n<div class=\"hear-what-inner\">\r\n<h3>Here’s what some of our clients have to say:</h3>\r\n<p></p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-thirds\">\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/penny.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>Worth every penny.</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n<p> “These folks are just fabulous. I enrolled today and already have my personal coach on the case for all kinds of things.  They are really brilliant and empathetic and like having a personal assistant to get things done.  Worth every penny!”</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/frustrating.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>My life has been less frustrating.</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n<p>“My life has been less frustrating and getting to be less stressful since I started talking to Nicole.  It’s nice to know that there are other people out there dealing with the same issues as a caregiver of a parent or close friend that is ill.”</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/fog.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>It feels like I am coming out of a fog.</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n<p>“Your advice in your last email was excellent. The more I hear it the more I can see more clearly. It feels like I am coming out of a fog after fixating on what is wrong vs. what can help. Thanks so much.”</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"coaches-feature\">\r\n        <div class=\"third coach\">\r\n               <div class=\"coach-pic\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_coach.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n               <div class=\"coach-name\"><h5>Marla</h5><h5>Senior Care Coach</h5></div>\r\n               <!-- <div class=\"coach-title\"><h5>Senior Care Coach</h5></div> -->\r\n               <div class=\"block\"><p>Marla joined CaregiverHQ in February of 2014, coming with over 22 years of industry experience. Marla is very passionate and dedicated to caregiving from both personal and professional experiences. Marla holds multiple degrees including a Master of Business Administration, a Master of Social Work, Licensed, with multiple industry certifications; a Healthcare Ethics Degree, and has completed the Pennsylvania State approved Nursing Home Administrator program.</p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"third coach\">\r\n		<div class=\"coach-pic\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_coach_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n                <div class=\"coach-name\"><h5>Nicole</h5><h5>Care Coach</h5></div>\r\n                <!-- <div class=\"coach-title\"><h5>Care Coach</h5></div> -->\r\n                <div class=\"block\"><p>Nicole is a Licensed Social Worker who joined the Highmark team in March of 2014. She received her Master’s Degree in Social Work at the University of Pittsburgh and has various experiences working with multiple cultures in the healthcare industry. Her experience includes working in hospice, skilled nursing facilities and mental health with a small stint in American Samoa as an Assistant Director at a local non-profit.</p></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"third coach\">\r\n		<div class=\"coach-pic\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_coach_3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n                <div class=\"coach-name\"><h5>Marcia</h5><h5>Care Coach</h5></div>\r\n                <!-- <div class=\"coach-title\"><h5>Care Coach</h5></div> -->\r\n                <div class=\"block\"><p>Marcia is a licensed clinical social worker with over 25 years’ experience working with adults, children and families. She enjoys her role as an adjunct instructor at the University of Pittsburgh Graduate School of Social Work teaching short-term therapy interventions and strategies. Marcia’s most recent position prior to joining the CaregiverHQ team was as a medical social worker providing assessment, support and resource coordination to patients awaiting transplant and their families.</p></div>\r\n       </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>", "Referals", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "104-revision-v1", "", "", "2015-01-25 14:38:53", "2015-01-25 14:38:53", "", "104", "http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/104-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("111", "1", "2015-01-25 17:29:16", "2015-01-25 17:29:16", "<div class=\"super-hero benefits\">\r\n 	\r\n	<div class=\"super-hero-inner\">\r\n			<div class=\"super-hero-callout reverse\">\r\n				<h2>CaregiverHQ Is Here For You,<br>So You Can Be There For Them.</h2>\r\n                                <p>Caring for a loved one means facing many difficult, stressful decisions that can weigh on your mind. Sometimes it may feel like a caregiver’s duties are never done. Each day brings about a new task list, and sometimes it can be overwhelming trying to balance everything you need to do. We know how selfless being a caregiver is, and that taking time for yourself may feel selfish to you. Let our experts lend you a helping hand to lift some of the burden off your shoulders and provide the caregiver support you deserve every step of the way.</p>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"paulund_modal\">Click Here</a>\r\n			</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n	<div class=\"left-half benefits-one\"></div>\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"right-half\">\r\n             <div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"title\"><h2>Personal Care Coach</h2></div>\r\n		<div class=\"block\"><p>You’ll be paired with a Personal Care Coach, a licensed social worker who meets your specific needs. Together, you’ll set achievable goals that your coach will proactively help you meet. When you’re not feeling wholly yourself, you’re not giving your whole self to any aspect of your life. With a Personal Care Coach available to counsel you, you can get back on track to a healthier, happier you.</p></div>\r\n             </div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"left-half\">\r\n             <div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"title\"><h2>Personal Caregiving Roadmap</h2></div>\r\n		<div class=\"block\"><p>Options for your loved one can seem endless. Our experts have answers to your questions – both logistical and emotional – so you can rest assured that you’re doing the right thing. Your care coach will create a “personal caregiving roadmap” to help you navigate through these options and plan to meet specific goals. We want to make sure your work as a caregiver is manageable and that you’re providing the best possible care you can give.</p></div>	\r\n             </div>						\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"right-half benefits-two\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n	<div class=\"left-half benefits-three\"></div>\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"right-half\">\r\n             <div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"title\"><h2>Premium Service Network</h2></div>\r\n		<div class=\"block\"><p>You may need a variety of services for your loved one – from in-home help to legal guidance. We know you may not have the time to research all of the services available in your area, so your Personal Care Coach will connect you to our network of service providers who have been evaluated by CaregiverHQ to guarantee the highest level of care.  </p></div>	\r\n             </div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-thirds\">\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"third\">\r\n               <div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n               <div class=\"title\"><h5>Premium Service Network</h5></div>\r\n               <div class=\"block\"><p>You may need a variety of services for your loved one – from in-home help to legal guidance. We know you may not have the time to research all of the services available in your area, so your Personal Care Coach will connect you to our network of service providers who have been evaluated by CaregiverHQ to guarantee the highest level of care.  </p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"third\">\r\n		<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n                <div class=\"title\"><h5>Personal Care Services</h5></div>\r\n                <div class=\"block\"><p>Does your loved one require in-home care beyond what you are able to provide alone? Trust CaregiverHQ to find high-quality personal care options for you.</p></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"third\">\r\n		<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n                <div class=\"title\"><h5>Legal</h5></div>\r\n                <div class=\"block\"><p>Whether you need a legal services for estate planning, writing a will, or just getting your loved one’s affairs in order – let our premium network of legal professionals help you.</p></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"inner-container bottom\">\r\n	<div class=\"third\">\r\n		<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_4.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n                <div class=\"title\"><h5>Financial</h5></div>\r\n                <div class=\"block\"><p>Here, members can find information on financial service providers, financial planning tips and more.</p></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"third\">\r\n		<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_5.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n                <div class=\"title\"><h5>Transportation</h5></div>\r\n                <div class=\"block\"><p>Your care coach can help you set up transportation to and from doctor’s appointments or the grocery store. Or, you can use our resources on your own.</p></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>", "Care Benefits", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "5-revision-v1", "", "", "2015-01-25 17:29:16", "2015-01-25 17:29:16", "", "5", "http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/5-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("114", "1", "2015-01-25 19:00:07", "2015-01-25 19:00:07", "<div class=\"container-thirds\">\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>Premium Service Network</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n<p>You may need a variety of services for your loved one – from in-home help to legal guidance. We know you may not have the time to research all of the services available in your area, so your Personal Care Coach will connect you to our network of service providers who have been evaluated by CaregiverHQ to guarantee the highest level of care.  </p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>Personal Care Services</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n<p>Does your loved one require in-home care beyond what you are able to provide alone? Trust CaregiverHQ to find high-quality personal care options for you.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>Legal</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n<p>Whether you need a legal services for estate planning, writing a will, or just getting your loved one’s affairs in order – let our premium network of legal professionals help you.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"inner-container bottom\">\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_4.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>Financial</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n<p>Here, members can find information on financial service providers, financial planning tips and more.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_5.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>Transportation</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n<p>Your care coach can help you set up transportation to and from doctor’s appointments or the grocery store. Or, you can use our resources on your own.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>", "Enroll", "", "trash", "closed", "closed", "", "enroll", "", "", "2015-01-25 20:15:50", "2015-01-25 20:15:50", "", "0", "http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/?post_type=modalpress&#038;p=114", "0", "modalpress", "", "0");
