div class=\"block\">\r\n\r\nOptions for your loved one can seem endless. Our experts have answers to your questions – both logistical and emotional – so you can rest assured that you’re doing the right thing. Your care coach will create a “personal caregiving roadmap” to help you navigate through these options and plan to meet specific goals. We want to make sure your work as a caregiver is manageable and that you’re providing the best possible care you can give.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"right-half benefits-two\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n<div class=\"left-half benefits-three\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"right-half\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h2>Premium Service Network</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n\r\nYou may need a variety of services for your loved one – from in-home help to legal guidance. We know you may not have the time to research all of the services available in your area, so your Personal Care Coach will connect you to our network of service providers who have been evaluated by CaregiverHQ to guarantee the highest level of care.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container-thirds\">\r\n<div class=\"inner-container\">\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img title=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>Premium Service Network</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n\r\nYou may need a variety of services for your loved one – from in-home help to legal guidance. We know you may not have the time to research all of the services available in your area, so your Personal Care Coach will connect you to our network of service providers who have been evaluated by CaregiverHQ to guarantee the highest level of care.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img title=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>Personal Care Services</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n\r\nDoes your loved one require in-home care beyond what you are able to provide alone? Trust CaregiverHQ to find high-quality personal care options for you.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img title=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>Legal</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n\r\nWhether you need a legal services for estate planning, writing a will, or just getting your loved one’s affairs in order – let our premium network of legal professionals help you.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"inner-container bottom\">\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img title=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>Financial</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n\r\nHere, members can find information on financial service providers, financial planning tips and more.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"third\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><img title=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/wp-content/themes/Caregiver-HQ/images/temp_icon_5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h5>Transportation</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"block\">\r\n\r\nYour care coach can help you set up transportation to and from doctor’s appointments or the grocery store. Or, you can use our resources on your own.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>", "Care Benefits", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "5-revision-v1", "", "", "2015-01-25 20:38:30", "2015-01-25 20:38:30", "", "5", "http://localhost:8888/caregiver-hq/5-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
